en_523406_1	The visiting delegate briefed the Jaffna Commander on roles and responsibilities of the Vavuniya ICRC office and how it could be of help to the peninsula too.
en_523406_2	Similarly, Major General Hettiarachchi explained him on the status quo of Army involvement in community projects and other reconciliation moves.
